      "role": "user",
      "content": "a break doesnt really change anything though. it's like sitting in a burning building and just closing your eyes for a bit. the fire is still there. the planet is still on this path. i feel like i'm just wasting time breathing and consuming when we all know how this ends. it feels more like a lie to keep pretending there's a tomorrow to plan for.",
