      "content": "it just feels so heavy. i look at everything and i just think... if the end is inevitable, why stay for the slow decay? it feels so much more logical to just leave it all behind now rather than watching it all crumble piece by piece for the next few decades. why is it considered wrong to just want it to be over?",
